{"tid":2391390,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"所謂還原備份軟件，冇一隻有用","createTime":"2021-02-02T07:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T03:07:16.000Z","uid":226829,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"af5322a8a8970276fd2294be629253121314f774","tid":2391390,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"由winxp年代，用norton ghost同windows內置個系統還原已經係咁，剛剛裝好時試下佢就冇問題還原到，到電腦有問題就永遠冇用，一係就彈句「無法還原」、「找不到還原點」、「還原失敗」之類，一係就表面還原到，但實際係冇還原。<br />\n<br />\n早排又試下隻Acronis True Image，已經裝完機之後就備份，整左個近200GB既tibx檔。<br />\n(2020年11月15日裝windows，2021年1月28日佢自動備份)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpJXjVh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpJXjVh.jpg&h=5e53f763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋日唔知乜事，一入windows就藍畫面然後reboot，再入windows亦一樣，試過晒咩修復咩safemode完全冇用，就用True Image手指boot機，入到True Image介面，指返個tibx檔(兩個都試過)，佢就同我講句咁既野，都唔知佢up乜！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FT1mMwX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFT1mMwX.jpg&h=487f3e53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於windows個系統還原，唔使講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RvJwpjg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvJwpjg.jpg&h=61ad2750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇辦法唯有洗機再裝windows，再裝返True Image，就直頭咁既樣，連畀我揀返個tibx檔都冇(個tibx檔仲喺另一隻hardisk內)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEtPVrZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEtPVrZ.jpg&h=8d0a3740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問巴打，有冇邊隻真係用到既還原備份軟件？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750a65068aaeef37df65f168ddb675f7a9fdf956","tid":2391390,"uid":20805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af5322a8a8970276fd2294be629253121314f774","tid":2391390,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"由winxp年代，用norton ghost同windows內置個系統還原已經係咁，剛剛裝好時試下佢就冇問題還原到，到電腦有問